text:
i'm very interested in knowing, the average amount of Bonus gained, as weighed against the time spent on this task

also:
i might opine, it would be helpful to us, The Taskers, if you could include a Progress Bar, so we can know how far-along we are

unless, of course, you were also interested in testing "something else" — which, the inclusion of such a (Quality of Life Improvement) would prevent your measuring
